    "description": "一小群叫做科学自由的恐怖分子在星球各处安设了力场。联合国度任命你手持一把锤子，穿戴我们所拥有的唯一一件坚不可摧盔甲，去阻止这一威胁。利用你的战斗技能，面对邪恶科学家控制之下的各种动物和机器人。 <br><br>使用锤子重击环境，将碎片打向敌人；或使用攻击和格挡技巧，将敌人击退。进行深思熟虑的战斗，熟悉敌人的行动以取得胜利 – 如果失败，就在敌人头上砸下去一堆东西吧。邪恶的科学家们控制着数之不尽的野兽，20 个以上的重重关卡妨碍着我们找出他们的邪恶计划。你，或者在你之后穿戴坚不可摧盔甲之人，是我们唯一的希望。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><br><strong>可破坏的交互式环境：</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/d364084a8a33594e7268cc9bb5891a40.poster.avif?t=1694185036\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/d364084a8a33594e7268cc9bb5891a40.webm?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/d364084a8a33594e7268cc9bb5891a40.mp4?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>方向性格挡和攻击：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/061ef96282f0e181bbb5131cae253bb9.poster.avif?t=1694185036\" width=172 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/061ef96282f0e181bbb5131cae253bb9.webm?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/061ef96282f0e181bbb5131cae253bb9.mp4?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><br><strong>反击：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/df48c21d6861f1249fb902ad4fcd7320.poster.avif?t=1694185036\" width=186 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/df48c21d6861f1249fb902ad4fcd7320.webm?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840820/extras/df48c21d6861f1249fb902ad4fcd7320.mp4?t=1694185036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特性</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>全面可破坏的环境。<br></li><li>突发性的游戏玩法和交互式环境。 <br></li><li>深思熟虑的战斗。了解敌人并作出对应行动。<br></li><li>种类繁多的敌人，超过 20 个关卡。 <br></li><li>基于技巧的战斗。不含角色发展，不掉落战利品。</li></ul>",
